faqs.question: What is Dhruv - Company Management System?
faqs.answer: It is a web-based system to manage company operations including employees, payroll, projects, performance, and more.

faqs.question: How do I log in to the system?
faqs.answer: Use your registered email or phone number and password on the login page. Ensure you enter the correct captcha.

faqs.question: What if I forget my password?
faqs.answer: Click on 'Forgot Password', enter your email, verify the OTP, and set a new password.

faqs.question: Can I register as an employee myself?
faqs.answer: Yes, fill in the register form with your details, and you will be assigned a department automatically.

faqs.question: How do I view my profile?
faqs.answer: Click on the 'Profile' page from the sidebar to view or edit your profile, change your photo or update password.

faqs.question: How can I apply for leave?
faqs.answer: Go to the 'Attendance' section and submit a leave request. It will be reviewed and approved by your manager.

faqs.question: Where can I view my payslips?
faqs.answer: Go to the 'Payroll' section. You can preview or download your monthly payslips there.

faqs.question: Can I be assigned to multiple projects?
faqs.answer: Yes, project managers can assign you to more than one ongoing project based on your department.

faqs.question: How is performance reviewed?
faqs.answer: Performance reviews are conducted monthly/quarterly with rating feedback and goal tracking visible in the 'Performance' section.

faqs.question: Is my personal information secure?
faqs.answer: Yes, your data is protected with secure authentication, encrypted storage, and role-based access.

faqs.question: How do admins manage departments?
faqs.answer: Admins can add/edit/delete departments and assign heads using the 'Departments' module.

faqs.question: How do I contact support?
faqs.answer: Use the 'Contact' page to submit a message. Choose your query type and the team will get back to you.

faqs.question: Can I edit my registered email?
faqs.answer: Yes, go to 'Profile' and update your email after OTP verification.

faqs.question: What technologies is this system built on?
faqs.answer: The system is built using Angular for frontend, Node.js/Express backend, and JSON Server or Swagger UI API.

faqs.question: How do I know if my leave is approved?
faqs.answer: Once reviewed, your leave status is updated in the 'Leave History' panel under 'Attendance'.

faqs.question: How do I reset my captcha if unreadable?
faqs.answer: Click the refresh icon next to the captcha input field to generate a new one.

faqs.question: What is the minimum password requirement?
faqs.answer: Passwords must be at least 8 characters long, contain uppercase, lowercase, number, and special character.

faqs.question: Can I view department sizes?
faqs.answer: Yes, department overview shows the number of active members in each department.

faqs.question: Can users delete their account?
faqs.answer: Yes, users can request profile deletion via the 'Profile' page. Admin approval may be required.

faqs.question: Is attendance auto-marked daily?
faqs.answer: Attendance must be marked manually by employees daily or synced via biometric integrations (if enabled).
